    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840880/extras/08a5aee3c17e99994aed4fceedc2cd13.avif?t=1763736607\" width=600 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840880/extras/24b3ebad7c63ba241992a29558ecf21c.poster.avif?t=1763736607\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840880/extras/24b3ebad7c63ba241992a29558ecf21c.webm?t=1763736607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840880/extras/24b3ebad7c63ba241992a29558ecf21c.mp4?t=1763736607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎进入疯狂的《冥舞之约》世界！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，地下城探索、恋爱模拟与节奏战斗完美融合，带来前所未有的火热体验。在《冥舞之约》的动感旋律里尽情起舞吧，多层次音乐系统将根据你的风格动态调整，打造你的专属节奏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840880/extras/7779fe2b1c4e90bb95d533a69b3dd1fb.poster.avif?t=1763736607\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840880/extras/7779fe2b1c4e90bb95d533a69b3dd1fb.webm?t=1763736607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840880/extras/7779fe2b1c4e90bb95d533a69b3dd1fb.mp4?t=1763736607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 9个多层关卡等你挑战 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一关都是程序生成，充满独特的遭遇战和隐藏房间。Rogue-lite风格的进度系统让每次游戏都耳目一新，还有大量武器与增益供你选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840880/extras/7c38de92a7f06110bc2667c3cc955297.poster.avif?t=1763736607\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840880/extras/7c38de92a7f06110bc2667c3cc955297.webm?t=1763736607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840880/extras/7c38de92a7f06110bc2667c3cc955297.mp4?t=1763736607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一批具有传奇色彩的人物渴望与你见面</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >等等，他们不是已经死了吗？……问题不大。无论如何，你可以通过数百个独特的剧情事件了解他们，并选择一个与你一起逃离炼狱。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840880/extras/7504cfc66bb47569b5e6f030c8754d8e.poster.avif?t=1763736607\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840880/extras/7504cfc66bb47569b5e6f030c8754d8e.webm?t=1763736607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840880/extras/7504cfc66bb47569b5e6f030c8754d8e.mp4?t=1763736607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不仅仅是恋爱模拟</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成支线任务和小游戏来赢得她们的好感，最终将你选中的“冥界女士”带上约会，作为你的最终奖励！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840880/extras/e10358efd67e449fe678d74c8625817e.poster.avif?t=1763736607\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840880/extras/e10358efd67e449fe678d74c8625817e.webm?t=1763736607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840880/extras/e10358efd67e449fe678d74c8625817e.mp4?t=1763736607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挑战地狱的统治者</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过数百个独特的剧情事件了解神秘的冥界及其居民，向地狱中的统治者发起挑战！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840880/extras/6c011653792e50c887b8afe25daa4761.avif?t=1763736607\" width=600 height=96 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840880/extras/33fdeef5df6bac0c9db50cf57d78d0b7.poster.avif?t=1763736607\" width=620 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840880/extras/33fdeef5df6bac0c9db50cf57d78d0b7.webm?t=1763736607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840880/extras/33fdeef5df6bac0c9db50cf57d78d0b7.mp4?t=1763736607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
